{"tid":1333160,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［裝備撚] 721齊練打狗捧法！12蚊可獲神裝！","createTime":"2019-07-19T14:51:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-20T15:20:02.000Z","uid":270333,"like":46,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"7257cf20cbaf95e7b17a9636498db29229e60afc","tid":1333160,"uid":270333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T14:51:33.000Z","msg":"本身想去living plaza買35蚊背囊，點知已經畀快手嘅巴絲掃曬，不過有驚喜失獲，發現咗個打機裝備神器<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/egwkGdS.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FegwkGdS.png&h=d6bac0d7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n只係12蚊一枝，但有一定重量，拎上手係實淨嘅，就力打落自己手都feel到痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n佢有分4個size嘅，不過39cm呢隻就最fit，好掌握得嚟又有一定長度，拎嚟耍打狗捧法真係一絕，仲可以隔段距離嚟揮棍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dJJK70o.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdJJK70o.png&h=b86861c7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n不過實測過，迪卡儂19蚊背囊係放唔落佢，可能要搵個大dd嘅袋喇，唔係到時突咗出嚟，畀人懷疑就唔好啦，明明大家都係想買幾枝返去組裝個層架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n最後，希望7 21係online game 到見大家，記得齊裝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"04e8469c730f3173cc01db6f46d28cb21652474d","tid":1333160,"uid":270333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T14:53:15.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dfca6b534fbf008f4e6b19090f0211dd0aaeae4e","tid":1333160,"uid":270333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T14:56:26.000Z","msg":"打錯字，係收獲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c79468cf46ceec33603aaedb07435a091e860d42","tid":1333160,"uid":89767,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score